thread.title: Students return to school two weeks after Florida massacre

title: Students return to school two weeks after Florida massacre
text:
Students return to school two weeks after Florida massacre Wednesday, February 28, 2018 - 00:35 
Students and teachers traumatized by one of the deadliest U.S. mass shootings ever are resuming classes on Wednesday for the first time since a gunman killed 17 people in their Florida high school two weeks ago. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
